title: Distant Lullaby (emissions#3 chipdisk)
info:
"distant lullaby"

for the emissions#3 chipdisk


(heavily downsampled)

a much longer remix upcoming..




one small spinning blue orb

a marble in the ocean of blackness
that extends far away beyond reason

far away beyond the swell of brief humanity

far away from home
